title: (FIXED) J.Williams - Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crysta
description:
This release is from the actual commercial disc. It fixes the issue with the last track, which appeared due to a mastering mistake on the promo first sent to shops and radio stations, which cut the final 9 seconds. Thanks to FlynnFlann for the original posting.
